<emphasis id="B922EAC3FFB2534225EAFC3F5D09B8C8" bold="true" box="[212,567,920,953]" pageId="3" pageNumber="434">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
The Sacha Guinea Pig has not yet been classified as a distinct species on The IUCN Red List. At the time of the last [UCN assessment, the Sacha Guinea Pig was included as a form of the Brazilian Guinea Pig (C. 
<taxonomicName id="4C564D52FFB2534221ACFC415BD9BF76" authorityName="Erxleben" authorityYear="1777" box="[1170,1255,998,1031]" class="Mammalia" family="Caviidae" genus="Cavia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="3" pageNumber="434" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="aperea">aperea</taxonomicName>
), but it was not named or formally assessed as a subspecies.
</paragraph>
